# Interview Questions

### What is Web Scraping?

Web Scraping is the process of automatically extracting data from websites using software programs.

### Which Python Libraries are used?

* Requests
* BeautifulSoup
* Scrapy
* Selenium
* Pandas

### Difference between BeautifulSoup and Selenium?

| BeautifulSoup   | Selenium           |
| --------------- | ------------------ |
| Static Websites | Dynamic Websites   |
| Faster          | Slower             |
| HTML Parsing    | Browser Automation |

### What is Robots.txt?

A file that specifies which parts of a website can be crawled or scraped.

